sequenceDiagram
    actor Client
    participant Frontend as Frontend React
    participant Gateway as API Gateway
    participant Order as Order Service
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant PDF as PDFKit

    Client->>Frontend: Clique "Télécharger PDF"
    Frontend->>Gateway: GET /api/invoices/order/:orderId/pdf
    Gateway->>Order: Proxy requête (JWT vérifié)
    Order->>Order: Vérifie ownership (userId ou ADMIN)
    Order->>Order: Récupère invoice + order + items + payment

    Order->>Auth: GET /api/users/:userId
    Auth-->>Order: {firstName, lastName, email, phone}

    Order->>PDF: Génère document A4
    Note right of PDF: En-tête Assiette Gala<br/>Infos client (nom, email, tel)<br/>Adresse de livraison<br/>Tableau des articles<br/>Sous-total, TVA 19%, livraison<br/>Total en DT<br/>Mode et statut paiement

    PDF-->>Order: Buffer PDF

    Order-->>Gateway: Content-Type: application/pdf
    Gateway-->>Frontend: Fichier PDF
    Frontend-->>Client: Téléchargement facture-INV-XXXXXX.pdf
